#How to create pools
You can create server pools in the services portion of the dhcp server under DHCP,
You select the gateway and dsubnet mask in association with the vlan if you are using vlans.
#working with serverPool, 
this will give a range of ip addresses that can work with, serverPool cannot be delted as you need a default range ot work with
#Assigning ip helper addresses
enable
config t
config interface vlan x
ip helper-address 'DHCP Server'
#any issues I encontered
none
